OL,3,CThousands expected to march through
OL,4,CLondon to demand cleaner water
OL,6,FThe March for Clean Water will see
OL,7,Fprotesters meet at the Albert
OL,8,FEmbankment on Sunday before heading
OL,9,Falong the River Thames to a rally in
OL,10,FParliament Square.
OL,12,FParticipants have been asked to bring
OL,13,Fa sample of the waters they love and
OL,14,Fto wear blue to form "a mass human
OL,15,Friver" on the march.
OL,17,FEnvironmental activist and singer
OL,18,FFeargal Sharkey, TV presenter Chris
OL,19,FPackham and adventurer Bear Grylls are
OL,20,Famong those expected to attend the
OL,21,Fevent.
