OL,3,CThousands expected to march through
OL,4,CLondon to demand cleaner water
OL,6,FThe campaign will call for an
OL,7,Fimmediate root and branch review of
OL,8,Fthe regulator Ofwat and the
OL,9,FEnvironment Agency, the stricter
OL,10,Fenforcement of existing laws and
OL,11,Fregulations on water pollution and
OL,12,Fensuring all polluting industries
OL,13,Finvest in upgrading infrastructure,
OL,14,Freducing water wastage and leakage and
OL,15,Fhelping farmers restore habitats.
