OL,3,CThousands expected to march through
OL,4,CLondon to demand cleaner water
OL,6,FThe Water (Special Measures) Bill, set
OL,7,Fout by the Government in Parliament
OL,8,Flast month, will aim to give
OL,9,Fregulators powers to issue harsher
OL,10,Fpenalties to water companies that
OL,11,Fdamage the environment, including
OL,12,Fsevere and automatic fines, blocked
OL,13,Fbonuses and even two-year prison
OL,14,Fsentences for uncooperative executives.
