OL,6,FA Southern Water spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We're preparing to deliver an
OL,8,Fambitious investment plan for the next
OL,9,Ffive years that matches what our
OL,10,Fcustomers have asked for - improving
OL,11,Fprotection of the environment, and
OL,12,Fensuring a reliable supply of clean
OL,13,Fwater for the region.
OL,15,F"Our bills have remained flat since
OL,16,F2014, so we will need to charge more
OL,17,Fto achieve these goals, but we'll
OL,18,Fcontinue supporting customers who may
OL,19,Fneed help with their bills, and will
OL,20,Fbe increasing that support.
